libcppdigest
------------------------------------------
C++ library for managing htdigest-like file

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libcppdigest-devel-0.2-1bl4
  libcppdigest0-0.2-1bl4
  libdigest0-0.2-1bl4
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libpcrecpp0-8.45-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libdigest-devel-0.2-1bl4
  libpcre-devel-8.45-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/digest/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/digest/libcppdigest-0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcppdigest-0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcppdigest-0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcppdigest-0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcppdigest-0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcppdigest0-0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcppdigest-devel-0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcppdigest)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcppdigest.README

(libcppdigest0)
  /usr/bin/cygcppdigest-0.dll

(libcppdigest-devel)
  /usr/include/cppdigest.h
  /usr/lib/libcppdigest.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libcppdigest.pc

------------------

